ingredients.ingredient: olive oil cooking spray (such as PAM®)
1 small butternut squash - peeled, seeded, and cut into French fry-like strips

cookingTips: Pat squash fries dry after cutting to reduce moisture and improve crispiness
Toss lightly with cooking spray for even coverage without excess oil
Bake at 400°F for 25-30 minutes, stirring halfway through for even browning
enrichment.coachingPrompt: What dipping sauces or seasoning blends would complement these roasted squash fries while keeping them healthy?
